Package processors

Interface IProcessor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Processor, ReverseProcessor, ShellProcessor
    public interface IProcessor
    Interface for an abstract "Processor", capable of taking a list of chunks, and "weaving" them into an output document that is emitted to a "destination" (a PrintStream).
